<body>
    <div class="container my-5">
        <h1 class="mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>

        <p>At Wanderlust, we value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your data when you visit our website.</p>

        <h3>Information We Collect</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><b>Personal Information:</b> Name, email address, phone number, and payment details when you make a booking or register on our platform.</li>
            <li><b>Usage Data:</b> Information on how you interact with our site, including IP address, browser type, and browsing behavior.</li>
            <li><b>Cookies and Tracking Technologies:</b> We use cookies to enhance your experience, analyze traffic, and personalize content.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>How We Use Your Information</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>To provide, operate, and maintain our website and services.</li>
            <li>To process transactions and send booking confirmations.</li>
            <li>To communicate with you, including customer support and promotional offers.</li>
            <li>To improve our website, analyze trends, and gather demographic information.</li>
            <li>To comply with legal obligations and protect against fraudulent activities.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Sharing Your Information</h3>
        <p>We do not sell your personal data. We may share your information with trusted third-party service providers who assist us in operating the website, conducting our business, or servicing you, provided they agree to keep your information confidential.</p>

        <h3>Cookies</h3>
        <p>Our website uses cookies to personalize content and ads, provide social media features, and analyze traffic. You can control cookie preferences through your browser settings.</p>

        <h3>Your Rights</h3>
        <p>You have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal information. To exercise these rights or ask questions about our Privacy Policy, please contact us at <a href="mailto:privacy@wanderlust.com">privacy@wanderlust.com</a>.</p>

        <h3>Security</h3>
        <p>We implement appropriate security measures to protect your data from unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction.</p>

        <h3>Changes to This Privacy Policy</h3>
        <p>We may update this Privacy Policy occasionally. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new policy on this page. Please review it periodically.</p>

        <p class="text-muted mt-5"><small>Last updated: September 24, 2025</small></p>
    </div>
